Use Case
	CreateAsteroid
Actors
System,Asteroid
Description
	The system creates asteroids in a set frequency. The asteroid is created with heading, speed, size and position
Main Course of Events
Asteroid	System
			1.The system checks if enough time has passed since last asteroid creation
2.The system creates an asteroid
3.the system sets heading, speed, size and position

Alternative Flow of Events
1.1 Not enough time has passed. Do nothing.